'''Aridal''' iga amudr amccakkʷ zzɣ afrruy n ifasiwen. D uridal iga abaraw n unɣal uggar n ku anawn n ifasiwn wiyyaḍ, tamazirt nns tlla zzɣ iẓẓlmḍ n tfṛiqt ar agmmuḍ anammas. D kkan-ttinn imudar ad ddren ula g uṛupa macc afuḍn mnck aya-d. Aridal iga amudr icttan inna yufa slawann akkʷ miḍṛuṣ acku iga g imudar  i bahra yecttan  ɣaylli ffaln imudar yaḍni zund uccen nɣ-d ar asn ittakʷr aynna yad gʷmrn, macc ula nttan ar igʷmmr kra n tikkal iɣ tid tiwi tizi d ar igʷmmr imsuṭṭḍen imẓẓin d ar ictta igumma d ibuxxucn, d ittussan mas-d anawn imqquṛn ar gʷmmrn imudar imqquṛn zund ilf.

